description: NPL Food Truck is bringing you nothing but the best of the best when you're craving great food on the go! Have you been craving a freshly made pulled pork sandwich? Strawberry chicken salad? Turkey pretzel club? All these, and so much more, are rolling down a street near you! Perfect for your every event, NPL Food Truck is ready and waiting to take your special day to the next level!
name: NPL Food Truck
